When Malala was in the hospital,

263
0:14:33.094,000 --> 0:14:36,000
and she was going through the severe pains

264
0:14:36.341,000 --> 0:14:38,000
and she had had severe headaches

265
0:14:38.861,000 --> 0:14:41,000
because her facial nerve was cut down,

266
0:14:42.049,000 --> 0:14:44,000
I used to see a dark shadow

267
0:14:44.501,000 --> 0:14:49,000
spreading on the face of my wife.

268
0:14:50.038,000 --> 0:14:56,000
But my daughter never complained.

269
0:14:56.139,000 --> 0:14:58,000
She used to tell us,

270
0:14:58.2,000 --> 0:15:,000
"I'm fine with my crooked smile

271
0:15:00.251,000 --> 0:15:02,000
and with my numbness in my face.

272
0:15:02.993,000 --> 0:15:04,000
I'll be okay. Please don't worry."

273
0:15:05.072,000 --> 0:15:07,000
She was a solace for us,

274
0:15:07.201,000 --> 0:15:09,000
and she consoled us.

275
0:15:12.12,000 --> 0:15:16,000
Dear brothers and sisters,

276
0:15:16.341,000 --> 0:15:18,000
we learned from her how to be resilient

277
0:15:18.963,000 --> 0:15:21,000
in the most difficult times,

278
0:15:22.268,000 --> 0:15:25,000
and I'm glad to share with you

279
0:15:25.276,000 --> 0:15:3,000
that despite being an icon

280
0:15:31.168,000 --> 0:15:33,000
for the rights of children and women,

281
0:15:33.997,000 --> 0:15:38,000
she is like any 16-year old girl.

282
0:15:39.29,000 --> 0:15:44,000
She cries when her homework is incomplete.

283
0:15:44.422,000 --> 0:15:46,000
She quarrels with her brothers,

284
0:15:46.49,000 --> 0:15:49,000
and I am very happy for that.

285
0:15:50.213,000 --> 0:15:52,000
People ask me,

286
0:15:52.616,000 --> 0:15:55,000
what special is in my mentorship

287
0:15:56.108,000 --> 0:15:58,000
which has made Malala so bold

288
0:15:58.648,000 --> 0:16:02,000
and so courageous and so vocal and poised?

289
0:16:03.14,000 --> 0:16:09,000
I tell them, don't ask me what I did.

290
0:16:09.415,000 --> 0:16:12,000
Ask me what I did not do.

291
0:16:13.276,000 --> 0:16:18,000
I did not clip her wings, and that's all.

292
0:16:18.533,000 --> 0:16:2,000
Thank you very much.

293
0:16:21.415,000 --> 0:16:26,000
(Applause)

294
0:16:26.911,000 --> 0:16:3,000
Thank you. Thank you very much. Thank you. (Applause)

